# Dataset

This project uses the **Airbnb Listings & Reviews** dataset from the **Maven Analytics Data Playground**.

### Dataset Information

- Listings: 279K+ Airbnb listings
- Reviews: 5.3M+ guest reviews
- Cities: 10 major cities
- Data Structure: Multiple tables (Listings & Reviews)

### Dataset Source

Maven Analytics Data Playground:
https://mavenanalytics.io/data-playground/airbnb-listings-reviews

Original Open Data Source:
https://insideairbnb.com/

> Note: The original dataset files are not included in this repository due to their large file size.
